## Configuration for Claude Desktop

Add to `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "remotion": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "chuk_motion.server", "stdio"],
      "env": {
        "MCP_STDIO": "1"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

